text.id: Those hours, that with gentle work did frame
text.tspan: Those hours, that with gentle work did frame

text.id: The lovely gaze where every eye doth dwell,
text.tspan: The lovely gaze where every eye doth dwell,

text.id: Will play the tyrants to the very same
text.tspan: Will play the tyrants to the very same

text.id: And that unfair which fairly doth excel;
text.tspan: And that unfair which fairly doth excel;

text.id: For never-resting time leads summer on
text.tspan: For never-resting time leads summer on

text.id: To hideous winter, and confounds him there;
text.tspan: To hideous winter, and confounds him there;

text.id: Sap checked with frost, and lusty leaves quite gone,
text.tspan: Sap checked with frost, and lusty leaves quite gone,

text.id: Beauty o'er-snowed and bareness every where:
text.tspan: Beauty o'er-snowed and bareness every where:

text.id: Then were not summer's distillation left,
text.tspan: Then were not summer's distillation left,

text.id: A liquid prisoner pent in walls of glass,
text.tspan: A liquid prisoner pent in walls of glass,

text.id: Beauty's effect with beauty were bereft,
text.tspan: Beauty's effect with beauty were bereft,

text.id: Nor it, nor no remembrance what it was:
text.tspan: Nor it, nor no remembrance what it was:

text.id: But flowers distilled, though they with winter meet,
text.tspan: But flowers distilled, though they with winter meet,

text.id: Leese but their show; their substance still lives sweet.
text.tspan: Leese but their show; their substance still lives sweet.
